songs.label: Rough Guide
songs.comments: Previously unreleasedThis deliriously earnest (and exclusive) mix fuses dub and yodelling.  I first heard this loose collective in the United States on National Public Radio at the precise synchronicity-charmed moment when they were to air a segment on my yodelling book.  Actress-yodeller Kutzkelina, from Germany's Harz Mountains, began yodelling at the age of 6 and then avoided the style to pursue her muse in Berlin, until she began re-applying yodelling to new projects.
